Use of OneSignal for emails and push notifications
In order to improve our communication with you, the users of the Hundeo app, and to provide you with timely updates, personalized offers and important information, we use OneSignal, a service for sending emails and push notifications.
Processed data
By using OneSignal, personal data such as email addresses, device IDs and usage data (e.g. time of receipt of a message and interaction with it) may be processed. This data allows us to personalize and optimize communication with you by ensuring that you receive relevant and timely information.
Purposes and legal bases of processing
The integration of OneSignal serves to increase the efficiency of our communication strategies and to implement a targeted notification system within our app. The processing of your data is based on your consent (Art. 6 para. 1 sentence 1 lit. a GDPR) or, if the communication is necessary for the provision of our contractual services, on the legal basis of contract fulfillment (Art. 6 para. 1 sentence 1 lit. b GDPR). In addition, we rely on our legitimate interest (Art. 6 para. 1 sentence 1 lit. f GDPR) to provide you with relevant information and updates.
